high_descs: Turn left and all the way around until you are facing the sink,
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn around and then turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door and slice the apple.
Put the knife in the microwave, placed, horizontally, in front of the apple with the yellow handle on the left and the knife tip pointed to the right.
In the microwave, pick up the back left piece of the apple and shut the microwave door.
Turn right for three steps, turn left to face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door, put the apple in the front center of the second shelf with the uncut side facing out, shut the refrigerator door, wait a few seconds and open the door, take out the apple and shut the door.
Turn left, take three steps and turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the apple to the top left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Using a knife, cut an apple, have all pieces in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter at the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn right, move to the counter at the microwave.
Cut the apple, in the microwave, into sections.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn right, move to the refrigerator.
Put the apple section into the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the counter at the microwave.
Put the apple section in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple section into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink with the lettuce in it.
Take one knife from the front of the sink.
Turn around the turn left to the microwave on the counter.
Cut the apple inside the microwave with the knife.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Take one apple slice from the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator on your left.
Put the apple slice inside the refrigerator then shut the door, open the door and remove the apple.
Turn left and walk to the microwave on your right.
Put the apple inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled apple slice inside the microwave.
